 the president of the World DanceSport Federation (WDSF).\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 358, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Tay\", \"score\": 0.9841953752540454, \"rank\": 0.016058336064283522, \"text\": \"Tay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Tay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Tay\"}, {\"begin\": 386, \"end\": 413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World DanceSport Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 415, \"end\": 419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the president\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The article reflects the author's opinions and not necessarily the views of CGTN.\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The article\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 433}, {\"ngram\": \"the author's opinions\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"not necessarily the views\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"CGTN\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was recently asked if a B-boy or B-girl could ever be considered in the same illustrious company as celebrated Olympians such as Usain Bolt, Michael Phelps, or Nadia Comaneci.\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 636, \"end\": 646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Usain Bolt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\"}, {\"begin\": 648, \"end\": 662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.707718731510848e-38, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}, {\"begin\": 667, \"end\": 681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadia_Com\\u0103neci\", \"score\": 0.9999999839878911, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nadia Comaneci\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadia_Com\\u0103neci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadia_Com\\u0103neci\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a B-boy or B-girl\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"the same illustrious company\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 603}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My answer was, and still is, an unequivocal yes.\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My answer\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"an unequivocal yes\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, as president of the global governing body overseeing breaking's Olympic journey, my opinion could be considered somewhat biased.\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"president\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"the global governing body\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 786}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking's Olympic journey\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 824}, {\"ngram\": \"my opinion\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But please hear me out.\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On August 9-10 at the Paris Olympic Games, 33 of the world's most talented breakers (16 B-boys and 17 B-girls) will compete for gold in one-on-one competitions known as \\\"battles\\\" at the iconic Place de la Concorde.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 1114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1093, \"end\": 1113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 0.9999999999790816, \"rank\": 2.1062769766566842e-11, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's most talented breakers\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"16 B-boys\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 994}, {\"ngram\": \"17 B-girls\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"one-on-one competitions\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1059}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"battles\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the sport was added to Paris 2024 back in 2020, one of the stated goals was to attract younger, more culturally diverse audiences.\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1144, \"end\": 1154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9215657029379545e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1130}, {\"ngram\": \"the stated goals\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"younger, more culturally diverse audiences\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1250}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With its obvious youth appeal and ties to hip-hop \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 breaking being one of the four founding pillars of the genre \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 this objective is clearly achievable.\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its obvious youth appeal\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"ties\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"hip-hop\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1301}, {\"ngram\": \"the four founding pillars\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"the genre\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"this objective\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Without any doubt, this August, the sport will resonate with people of all ages and backgrounds, surprising many along the way.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any doubt\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1477}, {\"ngram\": \"all ages\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1489}, {\"ngram\": \"backgrounds\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dance is, after all, one of the oldest human endeavors, practiced for thousands of years by civilizations in all corners of the world.\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dance\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"the oldest human endeavors\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1627}, {\"ngram\": \"civilizations\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"all corners\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1659}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simply put, it's in our DNA.\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our DNA\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is why I am convinced that even those who are completely unfamiliar with breaking, a style of dance that originated in New York City in the 1970s before evolving into a competitive sport, cannot help but be impressed by what they will see from our athletes in Paris.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1829, \"end\": 1842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.5368333656522345e-15, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 1970, \"end\": 1975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999940883, \"rank\": 5.827972134988652e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"even those\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"a style\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"dance\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1809}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1970s\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1855}, {\"ngram\": \"a competitive sport\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the only dance sport on the Olympic program, breaking offers a little something for everyone.\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only dance sport\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2001}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic program\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2024}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"a little something\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"First and foremost, it features explosive, improvisational moves, amazing artistry and impressive athleticism \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 all a reflection of each athlete's unique style and creativity.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"explosive, improvisational moves\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2139}, {\"ngram\": \"amazing artistry\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2157}, {\"ngram\": \"impressive athleticism\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2184}, {\"ngram\": \"all a reflection\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"each athlete's unique style\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2236}, {\"ngram\": \"creativity\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And because breakers cannot repeat dance moves, there is a layer of artistic unpredictability that audiences find captivating.\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2379, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"breakers\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"dance moves\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2299}, {\"ngram\": \"a layer\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"artistic unpredictability\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"audiences\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2361}, {\"ngram\": \"captivating\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An urban sport that can be organized practically anywhere, breaking is also the only sport on the Olympic Summer Games program where hip-hop and funk music form such an important part of the competition, giving sports fans a totally different and unique experience.\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2646, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An urban sport\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2395}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2448}, {\"ngram\": \"the only sport\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2471}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Summer Games program\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"hip-hop\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"funk music\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2536}, {\"ngram\": \"such an important part\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2583}, {\"ngram\": \"sports fans\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2603}, {\"ngram\": \"a totally different and unique experience\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And since our athletes do not know ahead of time what music the DJs will play, they must improvise on the spot each time they hit the dance floor, adding a sense of immediacy and excitement to the proceedings.\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2856, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2669}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2695}, {\"ngram\": \"what music\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2706}, {\"ngram\": \"the DJs\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"the spot\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2757}, {\"ngram\": \"the dance floor\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2792}, {\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2808}, {\"ngram\": \"immediacy\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2821}, {\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2836}, {\"ngram\": \"the proceedings\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, MCs are on hand to engage, educate and entertain audiences before, during and after the battles, elevating the atmosphere and keeping each event flowing smoothly.\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 3033, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2869}, {\"ngram\": \"MCs\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2874}, {\"ngram\": \"hand\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2886}, {\"ngram\": \"audiences\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2929}, {\"ngram\": \"the battles\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2966}, {\"ngram\": \"the atmosphere\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 2992}, {\"ngram\": \"each event\", \"from\": 3005, \"to\": 3015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking, therefore, is a rare sport that appeals to all the senses.\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Breaking\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3043}, {\"ngram\": \"a rare sport\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3071}, {\"ngram\": \"all the senses\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China's B-girl Liu Qingyi in action during Round 2 of Day 2 of the 2022 WDSF World Breaking Championship in Seoul, South Korea, Oct. 22, 2022.\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3105, \"end\": 3110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999375249919, \"rank\": 5.793117740495598e-08, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 3124, \"end\": 3130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qingyi_River_(Sichuan)\", \"score\": 0.6010059089230338, \"rank\": 0.4444444444445492, \"text\": \"Qingyi\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qingyi_River_(Sichuan)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qingyi_River_(Sichuan)\"}, {\"begin\": 3220, \"end\": 3231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 5.208759425229854e-12, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3140}, {\"ngram\": \"Round\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3153}, {\"ngram\": \"Day\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3162}, {\"ngram\": \"WDSF World Breaking Championship\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3209}, {\"ngram\": \"Seoul\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/Xinhua It is also a sport that is highly social media friendly.\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"/Xinhua\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3255}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3274}, {\"ngram\": \"highly social media\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During Breaking's first appearance at the Buenos Aires 2018 Summer Youth Olympic Games, for example, a video clip of the gold-medal-winning B-boy went viral, which eventually led to mentions in mainstream media outlets such as Sports Illustrated and The New York Times.\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3541, \"end\": 3559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.142554842573184e-14, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}, {\"begin\": 3564, \"end\": 3582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_New_York_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.465809848365515e-21, \"text\": \"The New York Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_New_York_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_New_York_Times\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Breaking's first appearance\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3348}, {\"ngram\": \"the Buenos Aires 2018 Summer Youth Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3352, \"to\": 3400}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3413}, {\"ngram\": \"a video clip\", \"from\": 3415, \"to\": 3427}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold-medal-winning B-boy\", \"from\": 3431, \"to\": 3459}, {\"ngram\": \"mentions\", \"from\": 3496, \"to\": 3504}, {\"ngram\": \"mainstream media outlets\", \"from\": 3508, \"to\": 3532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With an estimated global audience of well over a billion people expected to watch Paris 2024, there is every chance that one or more of our breakers will rocket into the social media stratosphere once again.\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3667, \"end\": 3677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9215657029379545e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an estimated global audience\", \"from\": 3590, \"to\": 3618}, {\"ngram\": \"well over a billion people\", \"from\": 3622, \"to\": 3648}, {\"ngram\": \"every chance\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 3700}, {\"ngram\": \"our breakers\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3733}, {\"ngram\": \"the social media\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3767}, {\"ngram\": \"stratosphere\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I believe this because I have witnessed first-hand the extraordinary upward trajectory of B-boys and B-girls around the world since 2016 when the World DanceSport Federation (WDSF) first accepted the invitation from the International Olympic Committee (IOC) to lead breaking's Olympic development.\", \"from\": 3794, \"to\": 4091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3940, \"end\": 3967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World DanceSport Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 3969, \"end\": 3973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 4014, \"end\": 4051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"first-hand the extraordinary upward trajectory\", \"from\": 3834, \"to\": 3880}, {\"ngram\": \"B-boys\", \"from\": 3884, \"to\": 3890}, {\"ngram\": \"B-girls\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 3902}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3910, \"to\": 3919}, {\"ngram\": \"the invitation\", \"from\": 3990, \"to\": 4004}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking's Olympic development\", \"from\": 4060, \"to\": 4090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The motivation to be part of the Olympic Games has resulted in incredible growth in terms of performance and organization.\", \"from\": 4093, \"to\": 4215, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The motivation\", \"from\": 4093, \"to\": 4107}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 4114, \"to\": 4118}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 4122, \"to\": 4139}, {\"ngram\": \"incredible growth\", \"from\": 4156, \"to\": 4173}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 4177, \"to\": 4182}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 4186, \"to\": 4197}, {\"ngram\": \"organization\", \"from\": 4202, \"to\": 4214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So much so that nobody \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 fans, judges, even fellow competitors \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 knows exactly what to expect from each breaker any longer, committed as they are to continually taking the sport to new, previously unimaginable heights.\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4438, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nobody\", \"from\": 4232, \"to\": 4238}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 fans\", \"from\": 4239, \"to\": 4247}, {\"ngram\": \"judges\", \"from\": 4249, \"to\": 4255}, {\"ngram\": \"even fellow competitors\", \"from\": 4257, \"to\": 4280}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093\", \"from\": 4281, \"to\": 4284}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 4291, \"to\": 4303}, {\"ngram\": \"each breaker\", \"from\": 4319, \"to\": 4331}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 4388, \"to\": 4397}, {\"ngram\": \"new, previously unimaginable heights\", \"from\": 4401, \"to\": 4437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the recent Olympic Qualifier Series (OQS) in Shanghai and Budapest (the final qualifier events for Paris 2024), the level of artistry, imagination and athleticism on display was quite simply jaw-dropping.\", \"from\": 4440, \"to\": 4647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4488, \"end\": 4496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 6.735693090019482e-13, \"text\": \"Shanghai\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\"}, {\"begin\": 4501, \"end\": 4509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.843757043789043e-15, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}, {\"begin\": 4542, \"end\": 4552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9215657029379545e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the recent Olympic Qualifier Series\", \"from\": 4443, \"to\": 4478}, {\"ngram\": \"OQS\", \"from\": 4480, \"to\": 4483}, {\"ngram\": \"the final qualifier events\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4537}, {\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 4555, \"to\": 4564}, {\"ngram\": \"artistry\", \"from\": 4568, \"to\": 4576}, {\"ngram\": \"imagination\", \"from\": 4578, \"to\": 4589}, {\"ngram\": \"athleticism\", \"from\": 4594, \"to\": 4605}, {\"ngram\": \"display\", \"from\": 4609, \"to\": 4616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The steady improvement of all aspects of breaking, both on the field of play and off, can be directly attributed to the sport's involvement in the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 4649, \"to\": 4810, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The steady improvement\", \"from\": 4649, \"to\": 4671}, {\"ngram\": \"all aspects\", \"from\": 4675, \"to\": 4686}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 4690, \"to\": 4698}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 4708, \"to\": 4717}, {\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 4721, \"to\": 4725}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport's involvement\", \"from\": 4765, \"to\": 4788}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 4792, \"to\": 4809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the WDSF has helped professionalize the sport and give it structure, the breaking community itself has embraced the Olympic spirit, as they can see that their culture can be adjusted to become a very exciting sport without losing its integrity or values.\", \"from\": 4811, \"to\": 5071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4821, \"end\": 4825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 4853, \"to\": 4862}, {\"ngram\": \"structure\", \"from\": 4875, \"to\": 4884}, {\"ngram\": \"the breaking community\", \"from\": 4886, \"to\": 4908}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 4929, \"to\": 4947}, {\"ngram\": \"their culture\", \"from\": 4970, \"to\": 4983}, {\"ngram\": \"a very exciting sport\", \"from\": 5010, \"to\": 5031}, {\"ngram\": \"its integrity\", \"from\": 5047, \"to\": 5060}, {\"ngram\": \"values\", \"from\": 5064, \"to\": 5070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This bodes extremely well for breaking's Olympic debut, and I cannot wait to see what kind of magic our 33 Olympians will conjure up on the Place de la Concorde with Olympic gold on the line.\", \"from\": 5073, \"to\": 5264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5213, \"end\": 5233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 0.9999999999790816, \"rank\": 2.1062769766566842e-11, \"te